(3,'LIBRETA DE REGISTRO DE SENTENCIAS -TURNO- (OFICIAL)','<p>se identificó que el campo \"FIRMA DE QUIEN RECIBE LAS CONSTANCIAS\" pertenece a un empleado del recinto</p>\r\n<p>CHANGELOG</p>\r\n<p>20170922 Separé el campo \"NOMBRE Y FIRMA DE RECEPCIÓN DE LAS CONSTANCIAS\" por \"NOMBRE DE QUIEN RECIBE LAS CONSTANCIAS\" Y \"FIRMA DE QUIEN RECIBE LAS CONSTANCIAS\"</p>\r\n<p>20171001 En reunión 29092017 con la DEGT se identificó que el campo \"FIRMA DE QUIEN RECIBE LAS CONSTANCIAS\" pertenece a un empleado del recinto por lo que se quitó el campo de captura \"NOMBRE DE QUIEN RECIBE LAS CONSTANCIAS\".</p>',2,0,'LIBRETA DE REGISTRO DE SENTENCIAS -TURNO','lsc01','ls01s','2','2s',4,'images/open_icon_library-standard/icons/png/16x16/actions/address-book-new.png','images/open_icon_library-standard/icons/png/48x48/actions/address-book-new.png','{\"generate_admin\":\"1\",\"generate_site\":\"1\",\"generate_site_views\":\"1\",\"generate_site_layout_article\":\"1\",\"generate_site_layout_blog\":\"1\",\"generate_admin_dashboard\":\"1\",\"generate_categories\":\"1\",\"generate_categories_site_views_categories\":\"1\",\"generate_categories_site_views_category\":\"1\",\"generate_plugins\":\"1\",\"generate_plugins_search\":\"1\",\"generate_plugins_finder\":\"1\",\"generate_plugins_itemnavigation\":\"1\",\"generate_plugins_vote\":\"1\",\"generate_plugins_pagebreak\":\"1\",\"generate_plugins_emailcloak\":\"1\",\"generate_plugins_loadmodule\":\"1\",\"generate_plugins_events\":\"1\",\"generate_modules\":\"1\"}','{\"include_access\":\"\",\"include_alias\":\"\",\"include_assetacl\":\"\",\"include_assetacl_record\":\"\",\"include_batch\":\"\",\"include_checkout\":\"\",\"include_copy\":\"\",\"include_created\":\"\",\"include_description\":\"\",\"include_featured\":\"\",\"include_hits\":\"\",\"include_image\":\"\",\"include_intro\":\"\",\"include_language\":\"\",\"include_metadata\":\"\",\"include_microdata\":\"\",\"include_modified\":\"\",\"include_name\":\"\",\"include_ordering\":\"\",\"includ