(8,'LIBRO DE CONTROL DE BILLETES Y PÓLIZAS (OFICIAL)','<p>Libro a nivel de la secretaria general de la sala.</p>\r\n<p>En la información proporcionada indicaron que \"SE REQUIERE DE FIRMA Y SE SUBDIVIDE EN AÑOS.\"</p>\r\n<p>Se requiere mayor información sobre la regla de negocios por la que se sub-divide la información en años, para visualizar la mejor forma de implementarlo.</p>\r\n<p>Sugiero cambiar el campo \"FIRMA \" por \"FIRMA DE A QUIEN SE DEVUELVE\"</p>\r\n<p>Salvador investigará a qué se refiere \"SE REQUIERE DE FIRMA Y SE SUBDIVIDE EN AÑOS.\"</p>\r\n<p>20170929 DEGT solicitó agregar el campo toral TOCA</p>',2,0,'LIBRO DE CONTROL DE BILLETES Y POLIZAS','lsc06','ls06s','2','2s',9,'images/open_icon_library-standard/icons/png/16x16/actions/address-book-new.png','images/open_icon_library-standard/icons/png/48x48/actions/address-book-new.png','{\"generate_admin\":\"1\",\"generate_site\":\"1\",\"generate_site_views\":\"1\",\"generate_site_layout_article\":\"1\",\"generate_site_layout_blog\":\"1\",\"generate_admin_dashboard\":\"1\",\"generate_categories\":\"1\",\"generate_categories_site_views_categories\":\"1\",\"generate_categories_site_views_category\":\"1\",\"generate_plugins\":\"1\",\"generate_plugins_search\":\"1\",\"generate_plugins_finder\":\"1\",\"generate_plugins_itemnavigation\":\"1\",\"generate_plugins_vote\":\"1\",\"generate_plugins_pagebreak\":\"1\",\"generate_plugins_emailcloak\":\"1\",\"generate_plugins_loadmodule\":\"1\",\"generate_plugins_events\":\"1\",\"generate_modules\":\"1\"}','{\"include_access\":\"\",\"include_alias\":\"\",\"include_assetacl\":\"\",\"include_assetacl_record\":\"\",\"include_batch\":\"\",\"include_checkout\":\"\",\"include_copy\":\"\",\"include_created\":\"\",\"include_description\":\"\",\"include_featured\":\"\",\"include_hits\":\"\",\"include_image\":\"\",\"include_intro\":\"\",\"include_language\":\"\",\"include_metadata\":\"\",\"include_microdata\":\"\",\"include_modified\":\"\",\"include_name\":\"\",\"include_ordering\